sec.p:
Starting from the precipitated OOPS interface, proteins were digested using 1μg Lys-C (Promega, Madison, WI, USA) in 100 μL of 100 mM TEAB (Sigma-Aldrich) with 1 μL of RNAseOUT (Thermo Fisher Scientific) overnight at 37 °C. Two different approaches were used to enriched RNA-peptides:


Silica-based RNA purification using the RNeasy kit (Qiagen), according with the manufacturer’s instructions;

Precipitation in 80% ethanol. Two rounds of precipitations were used to further clean the sample.
